{"tid":52313,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[毒撚悲歌]除左聖誕快樂，我都唔知講咩好","createTime":"2016-12-24T03:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T16:58:35.000Z","uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ac951d84218e7e924bf9f7dc3fffbed6165cb9d","tid":52313,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:24:40.000Z","msg":"其實一個人過聖誕又有乜可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說本身諗住畫幾張聖誕卡黎送，但畫得一張我就放棄了，反正都冇人想要，嘿。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/111230_ee1950daa6a685ed439c60f95331c2c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F111230_ee1950daa6a685ed439c60f95331c2c0.jpg&h=c13f0b1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真毒嘅大家要堅強，過多幾十個鐘就完架啦，merry christmas <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4345f4a098c6095c9ef12223a95773b3dcd5dee8","tid":52313,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"嘿，毒撚開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6085787b1cdce0f6c2afe3aba3db9c6baab6606b","tid":52313,"uid":178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:41:47.000Z","msg":"捱多三十六個鐘就完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca18d9f96fa596044adf7fcdce49528a992e23c4","tid":52313,"uid":15530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:42:34.000Z","msg":"諗住今晚一覺訓到26號<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a22505550a223570c9736ea8dd62d7cbdba9e0","tid":52313,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m4325O3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm4325O3.jpg&h=3e5b0b0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dec7edad768330843aa4b57843724f7ee9be1271","tid":52313,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:55:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捱多三十六個鐘就完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇錯，好快就過，你地要堅強<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8bc48dbb5f1ddbd017c02ec9d65eb2f708e0b1c","tid":52313,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:55:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗住今晚一覺訓到26號<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不失為一個好方法"},{"pid":"65b22fd0c2e98205189e04f1969a67f106390852","tid":52313,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多偽毒"},{"pid":"dc72ce35c543c4fb2879988acb31b4e8a8fafecc","tid":52313,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:13:48.000Z","msg":"自推到聖誕完，好想食拉麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500874f6356ef5d3f247f7ed427f7d22e9f685f9","tid":52313,"uid":2937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:16:03.000Z","msg":"根本唔洗捱 真毒已看透"},{"pid":"e90adcbd8dd5aef62f0ad26fa488cb8191b2d06b","tid":52313,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:41:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本唔洗捱 真毒已看透</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我也已看透，但好多人尚未習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b9d75916a3792a8a26f165bc98790f6c0b484a","tid":52313,"uid":9436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:57:51.000Z","msg":"兔仔卡好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三點都未想起身 起嚟唔知做咩<br />\n打算瞓晒四日假"},{"pid":"ed662a1a2927b1e3544bd4ba7cb5d7bb70550d58","tid":52313,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:49:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兔仔卡好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三點都未想起身 起嚟唔知做咩<br />\n打算瞓晒四日假</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我八點起左身到依家都未食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd13e62c0eb01b288e0962267bfe638a7bc67eb","tid":52313,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T10:14:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe547de37750d9761b829668174655dc1d21b64","tid":52313,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T10:43:54.000Z","msg":"可惡你地班偽毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4897d8afe573b8eb37b44332fe518bf0b742db3","tid":52313,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:58:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}